{
  "stem": "4284.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you looked like something from outer space because you had no hair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You're certainly not going to be inconspicuous in a crowd of people if you should escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And escape was just simply not possible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That simply-- that is just a physical impossibility.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The surrounding camp and then a perimeter of additional fortification just wasn't a way to escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was given B-7648.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was put on a truck, two trucks, about 60 people, 60 children, you know, less room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we drove approximately five, six, maybe 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from Birkenau, we were then transported and released in the actual concentration camp of Auschwitz, which was a separate and distinct, different, real concentration camp, versus the extermination facility of Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The smell and the odor, of course, all these crematorium that were working full time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Auschwitz, in the camp, there was no crematorium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was nothing there intended to kill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Beatings, yes, but no systematic-- that was done the five kilometers or whatever distance it was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we arrived there, we found out that we had each to share bunks, while in Birkenau, we just laid on the floor.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So you didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was quite a step up, and you felt like you have a place to sleep.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were three bunks high on straw, no pillows, and some rags, which if you want to call it blankets, it's a misnomer, but it's-- lice-infested, vermin all over the place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was something else than from what we had come.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
